thread.title: Fallout from Larry Nassar scandal as more victims testify

title: Fallout from Larry Nassar scandal as more victims testify
text:
Fallout from Larry Nassar scandal as more victims testify 10:34am IST - 01:25 
All directors of USA Gymnastics have now resigned and students are criticizing Michigan State University's Board of Trustees, as longtime doctor Larry Nassar goes back to court for abusing athletes under his care. Jillian Kitchener reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
